{"text_id":177840,"tokens":["Summer"," assignments"," can"," be"," an"," effective"," way"," for"," students"," to"," stay"," sharp"," and"," hone"," their"," skills"," over"," the"," summer"," months","."," However",","," the"," key"," to"," successful"," summer"," assignments"," lies"," in"," their"," level"," of"," engagement"," and"," productivity","."," The"," ideal"," approach"," to"," summer"," assignments"," depends"," upon"," whether"," they"," are"," teacher","-","designed"," or"," student","-","designed",","," as"," each"," approach"," entails"," different"," benefits"," and"," drawbacks",".","\n\n","When"," it"," comes"," to"," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments",","," the"," key"," advantage"," is"," that"," they"," are"," structured"," and"," organized",","," which"," means"," students"," can"," easily"," plan"," out"," how"," to"," complete"," the"," assignments"," in"," a"," timely"," and"," meaningful"," way","."," Moreover",","," since"," the"," assignments"," are"," typically"," planned"," in"," advance",","," students"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," stay"," on"," track"," with"," their"," work","."," Furthermore",","," teacher","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," are"," usually"," more"," rigorous"," and"," informative",","," as"," they"," are"," designed"," with"," specific"," educational"," objectives"," in"," mind","."," However",","," the"," drawbacks"," of"," this"," approach"," are"," that"," students"," may"," find"," the"," tasks"," to"," be"," mundane"," or"," uninteresting",","," and"," as"," a"," result",","," their"," engagement"," will"," likely"," suffer",".","\n\n","In"," comparison",","," student","-","designed"," summer"," assignments"," offer"," a"," certain"," level"," of"," flexibility"," that"," teacher","-","designed"," assignments"," lack","."," This"," allows"," students"," the"," freedom"," to"," pursue"," topics"," of"," interest",","," which"," can"," help"," to"," increase"," engagement"," signific